fm: EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode TelBLL_CM_ReadLockInfo(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo* param) {     EBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_FAILURE;  	if(NULL == param) 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Param Error"); 	    return ret; 	} 	 	if(NULL != telfunc_lockstsShm) 	{ 		memcpy(param, &telfunc_lockstsShm, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo)); 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Lock type [%d]", telfunc_lockstsShm->type); 		ret = eBTSRV_CM_ReturnCode_SUCCESS; 	} 	else 	{ 		BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Error :Shared memory is not opend"); 	}     return ret; }

void* BT_Service_CreateShm( char* shmPath ) {     int32_t fd = -1;     int32_t ret = -1;     void* addr = NULL;     bool bCreate = false;      // ���L�������̍쐬     fd = shm_open( shmPath, O_RDWR, 0777 );     if( fd < 0 ) {         // �����ݎ�         if (ENOENT == errno) {             // ����             fd = shm_open( shmPath, O_CREAT | O_RDWR, 0777 );             if( fd < 0 ) {                 return NULL;             }             bCreate = true;             // ���L�������̃T�C�Y�ύX             ret = ftruncate( fd, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo));             if( ret < 0) {                 return NULL;             }         } else {             return NULL;         }     }      // ���L���������v���Z�X�̉��z��ԂɃ}�b�s���O     addr = mmap( 0, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo), PROT_READ | PROT_WRITE, MAP_SHARED, fd, 0 );     if( addr == MAP_FAILED ) {         return NULL;     }      // �����������̓��������N���A����     if (bCreate) {         memset(addr,0x00, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo));     }      return addr; }

void BT_Service_writeShm( BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo* data ) { 	if(NULL != data) 	{ 		if(NULL != telfunc_lockstsShm) 		{ 			memcpy(telfunc_lockstsShm, data, sizeof(BTSRV_CM_Tel_Func_LockInfo)); 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Lock Status update to [%d]", telfunc_lockstsShm->type); 		} 		else 		{ 			BTSRV_PUBLIC_LOG(ZONE_BT_INFO,__PRETTY_FUNCTION__,"Error :Shared memory is not opend"); 		} 	} }
